  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    UpdateChecker.VersionScheme

    AlchemaConstants
    Various constants for the Alchema plugin.

    A utility class to more easily call the various events in Alchema.

    Represents a blacklist of EntityTypes refreshable from a Supplier.

    NamespacedKeyUtil
    A utility class to better handle NamespacedKey objects.
    UpdateChecker
    A utility class to assist in checking for updates for plugins uploaded to SpigotMC.
